Data Tables are an element meant to organize data on a page with added functionality such as sorting, filtering, and pagination. Evolution data tables depend on Foundation's [Tables](http://foundation.zurb.com/sites/docs/v/5.5.3/components/tables.html) as a starting point. The interactive elements of the data table (sorting, filtering, pagination, etc.) depend on [DataTables](http://datatables.net/) jQuery Plugin and Foundation's [Pagination](http://foundation.zurb.com/sites/docs/v/5.5.3/components/pagination.html) component.
